longBusinessSummary: Swaraj Engines Limited manufactures and sells diesel engines, diesel engine components, and spare parts for tractors in India. The company was incorporated in 1985 and is based in Mohali, India. Swaraj Engines Limited is a subsidiary of Mahindra & Mahindra Limited.
